{"tid":1946836,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"感慨..買樓心事) 樓愈黎愈多，但朋友就愈黎愈少","createTime":"2020-03-28T01:19:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-28T08:24:46.000Z","uid":82845,"like":2,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"bd9fe51a1d468fba04d76f8d8c44f1f371a29346","tid":1946836,"uid":82845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T01:19:51.000Z","msg":"以前嘅同伴，一個一個比我拋離<br />\n樓越多人就越孤獨。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n或者你會說人應重情不重錢。<br />\n沒錯，情比錢重要。<br />\n但我窮的時候卻沒人跟我重情。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我的第一間物業在20年前港島一個富豪地段。<br />\n那時我錢不多，還是勒緊肚皮買了下來。<br />\n此時友情開始回來了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n「我知你係掂嘅！兄弟！」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n兄弟？我在灣仔酒吧被圍時，<br />\n打電話找你求救，你怎回應我？虛偽。<br />\n<br />\n不用多久，我買了第二間物業。<br />\n朋友又變多了，「朋友！我地拍住上！」。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上你老鼠？我失戀想你陪我飲酒，你去那了？<br />\n<br />\n最後，我接近20間物業，包括山頂豪宅。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n朋友更多如牛毛，「兄弟！.....」<br />\n「停！不用說了，我從被世俗拋棄開始，就沒有兄弟。」我眼泛淚光，飲著茅台回答。<br />\n<br />\n嗯，樓越多，朋友越少。<br />\n談心的人更是沒有。<br />\n只能上上連登找樂趣。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但我不介意，反正世間無情，那何不只談錢？<br />\n沒樓的人，連跟我說半句話的資格都沒有。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\neg.純抒發下，100%真事"},{"pid":"1306b3e5b9e527c489b3da54824d2ac5d6cd06ee","tid":1946836,"uid":125168,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T01:25:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TMT7FX6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTMT7FX6.jpg&h=b618f014&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f7b939315afa0e528cd28c6279dde7116aa2813d","tid":1946836,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T01:25:53.000Z","msg":"樓主你好<br />\n我想做你朋友